{"tid":941030,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誕節GP, 窮撚勿入","createTime":"2018-12-14T12:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T06:40:12.000Z","uid":22975,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2c3e3e18e89a67c0894e2a96864b46f53388e35f","tid":941030,"uid":22975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:08:12.000Z","msg":"是咁的，呢個星期五，我唔去浦了。夜晚開Gay Party。 <br />\n我地book了3隻鴨。第一隻 黑人Drake  , 租的。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dP1mnd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdP1mnd7.jpg&h=9c209cc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lgkm6FR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgkm6FR.jpg&h=50946172&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大大隻，體力好可以搞成晚，長40幾CM粗6CM。 <br />\n<br />\n另一隻, 私伙的  Fern&aacute;ndez 西班牙人<br />\n粗獷成熟，標準洋腸，長30幾CM粗5CM。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RWFqOXe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRWFqOXe.jpg&h=39e0047e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OaJjToU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOaJjToU.jpg&h=d73af0cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZRRdXQA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZRRdXQA.jpg&h=d3c45737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我鍾意呢隻多d，唔會太大，入黎岩岩好。<br />\n<br />\n重有一隻普通亞洲人。<br />\n<br />\n搞手會買好多套，KY。 <br />\n<br />\n12月25號 , 7點重慶大廈集合 <br />\n<br />\n靚仔大隻大支野：$1000 位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑人，白人：Model , 靚仔免費。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牙籤仔毒撚：唔俾去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n來吧靚仔，識d俾得起$1000去Gay Party的人吧。 <br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢d Gay Party無得賺，搞手只求打個和，大家開開心心玩返晚。"},{"pid":"31a763f7a8951d91152e3aa0918c89b8111ec2ca","tid":941030,"uid":22975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img s